# Ghana Community & EA-Level Data Construction (GLSS4)

This project builds a unified **Enumeration Area (EA)-level community dataset** from multiple GLSS4 community modules (`cs0`–`cs5b`, `sec0`, `sec1`, `sec2`, `cs3`, `cs4a/b/c`) to support analysis of **agricultural profit per acre** and its relationship with local infrastructure, education, health environment, and agricultural inputs.

All source data are provided in **Stata `.dta` format** and are cleaned and aggregated in **R** to a consistent EA-level structure, with harmonized IDs and standardized binary coding.

---

